{
  "page": "Aemon (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Maekar_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Maekar I)\">Aemon</a></b> is the maester at Castle Black.\n</p><p>Other characters named <b>Aemon</b> include:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Blackfyre\" title=\"Aemon Blackfyre\">Aemon Blackfyre</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Costayne\" title=\"Aemon Costayne\">Aemon Costayne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Estermont\" title=\"Aemon Estermont\">Aemon Estermont</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Rivers\" title=\"Aemon Rivers\">Aemon Rivers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Steelsong\" title=\"Aemon Steelsong\">Aemon Steelsong</a>, also known as Aemon Battleborn</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Jaehaerys_I)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Jaehaerys I)\">Aemon Targaryen</a>, second son and third child of King Jaehaerys I and Queen Alysanne Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemon_Targaryen_(son_of_Viserys_II)\" title=\"Aemon Targaryen (son of Viserys II)\">Aemon Targaryen</a>, called the <i>Dragonknight</i>, second son and child of King Viserys II Targaryen and Larra Rogare</li></ul>\n<p>Additionally, <b>Aemon</b> can refer to:\n</p>\n<ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Prince_Aemon\" title=\"Prince Aemon\">Prince Aemon</a></i>, a galley</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aemon_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Aemond_Targaryen\" title=\"Aemond Targaryen\">Aemond Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Emmon_Cuy\" title=\"Emmon Cuy\">Emmon Cuy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Emmon_Frey\" title=